{"tid":768431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：期望外國記者會尊重香港是中國一部分","createTime":"2018-08-05T11:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T11:51:37.000Z","uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"66dca716b39871e7cfc6395edc5676c4816a4956","tid":768431,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥回應本港的外國記者會，邀請香港民族黨召集人陳浩天在午餐會演講，說機構以港獨為主題安排活動並不適合，對此表示非常可惜和遺憾，又指政府遏制港獨，與言論自由扯不上關係，要依法才可享有自由。她說，外國記者會租用的會所是政府物業，特區政府一直收取市值租金，她尊重海外傳媒工作，希望外國記者會在香港的活動，同樣尊重香港特區是中華人民共和國不可分割的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，政府對港獨議題立場堅定，絕不含糊，港府會全面落實一國兩制，維護國家安全、主權及領土完整，會依法遏制港獨。她不會評論保安局根據社團條例，考慮禁止香港民族黨運作的個案，保安局應當事人要求延長了申述時間，個案正處於法律過程，加上行政長官會同行政會議是處理上訴的機構，她現階段更加不適合評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1022884\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1022884&d=rJonw%2FOR30HaaENIyD0zgi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=f0bde639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1022884</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國外交部<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba583c8565db86d3f35941da65a0fe03c87d37c7","tid":768431,"uid":62815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T11:35:39.000Z","msg":"外媒:關你撚事"},{"pid":"d70ea29d3dc7325e0d14de41a276b2470cba2011","tid":768431,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T11:51:37.000Z","msg":"叫保安局取締埋佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}